page.title: 04A TYPICAL DAY
page.content: A typical day for me would be to get up at 7.45 brush my teeth and wash my face then I get dressed and go downstairs at about 8.00 for my breakfast. I normally have bacon friedbread and a drink of water. At 8.45 I go and call for my freind. Then we walk to school together. At 9.00 I go into school I spend the morning doing Maths and English, at 10.30 we have a playtime. I play with my friend Vicky. We play join up stag which is when one person is on and when they tig someone they have to join on to the person who is on. At 12.00 we have dinner we usually have chips, beans and sausage roll. At 1.30 we go in and we get changed for games.
